Brown is a common color in nature. It predominates the landscape and many animals have brown hair. The color is found in everyday surroundings in all of its various shades. In this video, CGTN Nature presents the beauty of the color brown. Check it out! The Colors of Nature This series combines music, color and natural scenery to give viewers a sensory experience. For more: Snowy Kanas in NW China's Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region The beauty of yellow sand The beauty of the color black (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)